Anyone having problem starting it?Go to the folder called Razor1911 in the iso file. 
There you will find a file called War3. 
After you found it go to the place you installed Warcraft 3, you may find a shortcut on your desktop, right click and go propertise. 
Click find target. 
There you will find all the Warcraft files, open the iso again and find the folder called Razor1911. 
Drag the file called War3 into your Warcraft 3 folder. Click yes when you get the message ''Do you want to replace this file''.
Click at the War3 file and PLAY MY FRIEND!!!:)
